metadata.description: Skadi is the beautiful Jotun goddess of winter, skiing, bow hunting and mountains. Skadi's name is remembered in Scandinavia which can be translated to "Skadi's Land." She is know as a strong, athletic, tall woman traveling through the harsh winter landscape. She may rescue you from a winter storm one day, This is Skadi.
